OL,7,FA former police officer from Weston-
OL,8,Fsuper-Mare is facing a hearing over
OL,9,Faccusations he had sex with a
OL,10,Fvulnerable woman whilst on duty.
OL,12,FPC Alexander Alderson, who was based
OL,13,Fin Weston-super-Mare, faces a
OL,14,Fmisconduct hearing at Avon & Somerset
OL,15,FConstabulary headquarters in
OL,16,FPortishead on Tuesday 26 March.
